google_544.nl_query: What is the display name of the user who last edited the post "Examples for teaching: Correlation does not mean causation"? "Examples for teaching: Correlation does not mean causation" is the Title of post; user who last edited refers to LastEditorUserId
google_544.golden_query: SELECT T2.DisplayName FROM posts AS T1 INNER JOIN users AS T2 ON T1.LastEditorUserId = T2.Id WHERE T1.Title = 'Examples for teaching: Correlation does not mean causation'
